1
00:00:00,458 --> 00:00:01,960
What are you saying?

2
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:03,753
That you like me?

3
00:00:04,045 --> 00:00:05,046
Oh, Shit!

4
00:00:07,132 --> 00:00:08,842
My report...

5
00:00:08,842 --> 00:00:12,220
'In conclusion, going further back into the past failed'

6
00:00:12,220 --> 00:00:14,931
'It seems the time I can return to is fixed'

7
00:00:14,931 --> 00:00:17,642
'Judging by the disappearance of another string on the bracelet'

8
00:00:17,642 --> 00:00:19,310
'I now have four chances left'

9
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:21,396
'I wasted a precious opportunity'

10
00:00:23,398 --> 00:00:24,983
'But still...'

11
00:00:24,983 --> 00:00:26,735
'I did manage to sneak a peck'

12
00:00:26,736 --> 00:00:29,610
[Third Time Loop]

13
00:00:29,738 --> 00:00:32,574
'Ah, I don't know anymore. It's all or nothing now'

14
00:00:32,574 --> 00:00:34,743
Yeah, I like you

15
00:00:34,743 --> 00:00:36,119
What, am I not allowed to like you?

16
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:38,872
No, that's not what I mean

17
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,999
What, what, will you wear out if I like you?

18
00:00:40,999 --> 00:00:44,878
What's so great about you? What's so amazing?

19
00:00:45,336 --> 00:00:46,337
Your face...

20
00:00:49,716 --> 00:00:51,968
Well, you're handsome...

21
00:00:51,968 --> 00:00:53,053
Your personality...

22
00:00:59,184 --> 00:01:01,102
Your personality is good too

23
00:01:01,102 --> 00:01:02,645
Then your body...

24
00:01:08,109 --> 00:01:10,278
Ah, never mind

25
00:01:10,987 --> 00:01:13,656
But isn't it my freedom to like you?

26
00:01:14,324 --> 00:01:15,950
So, why all of a sudden?

27
00:01:16,367 --> 00:01:17,535
Sudden?

28
00:01:17,535 --> 00:01:19,662
It's not sudden

29
00:01:19,662 --> 00:01:21,956
You said if neither of us gets a lover, we'd live together

30
00:01:21,956 --> 00:01:24,042
You said that first. Is this my fault?

31
00:01:24,042 --> 00:01:26,377
Then you shouldn't have been so nice to me

32
00:01:34,010 --> 00:01:36,513
'Ah... I overdid it...'

33
00:01:42,268 --> 00:01:43,770
Oh, Shit!

34
00:01:43,771 --> 00:01:46,509
[Fourth Time Loop]

35
00:01:52,779 --> 00:01:54,030
Hey, Ju-chan

36
00:01:56,074 --> 00:01:57,450
Just...

37
00:01:57,450 --> 00:01:59,452
Can’t you just pretend you didn’t hear that?

38
00:01:59,911 --> 00:02:01,788
Pretend I didn't hear?

39
00:02:02,789 --> 00:02:04,082
Does that make sense right now?

40
00:02:05,250 --> 00:02:07,252
No, look...

41
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:11,714
You and I have been friends for seven years

42
00:02:11,923 --> 00:02:14,342
Think about the friendship,

43
00:02:14,342 --> 00:02:17,428
connections, money, and time we've built up

44
00:02:17,428 --> 00:02:19,389
Let's say I confessed to you

45
00:02:19,389 --> 00:02:21,099
And you rejected it

46
00:02:21,099 --> 00:02:22,267
Then what happens to us?

47
00:02:23,643 --> 00:02:25,603
Of course, it gets awkward

48
00:02:25,603 --> 00:02:28,314
Then we can't hang out with Myung-wan, Jin-tae, and Cheol-min together

49
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:29,816
The seven years we've built?

50
00:02:29,816 --> 00:02:31,401
It all goes down the drain

51
00:02:32,443 --> 00:02:34,112
What are you even saying?

52
00:02:34,112 --> 00:02:34,904
Are you crazy?

53
00:02:36,114 --> 00:02:37,115
Right

54
00:02:37,115 --> 00:02:38,700
This is a bit crazy

55
00:02:41,536 --> 00:02:43,955
Not a lover...

56
00:02:45,790 --> 00:02:47,792
Then a friend...

57
00:02:47,792 --> 00:02:48,835
If even being friends is hard,

58
00:02:50,295 --> 00:02:52,297
then just a workout buddy...​

59
00:02:52,297 --> 00:02:55,133
Or, like, your pet dog at home..
No, wait, I’m still human, so maybe…

60
00:02:55,592 --> 00:02:56,759
Your pet human

61
00:02:57,677 --> 00:03:00,638
Or just… someone you know really well

62
00:03:01,014 --> 00:03:02,557
Anything’s fine

63
00:03:03,516 --> 00:03:05,393
Can’t we just…

64
00:03:05,393 --> 00:03:08,021
keep seeing each other like this?

65
00:03:08,563 --> 00:03:11,316
Do you think that makes sense?

66
00:03:11,316 --> 00:03:13,484
Do you think you and I can do that?

67
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:21,451
After hearing something like that…

68
00:03:21,451 --> 00:03:23,786
How am I supposed to stay just friends with you?

69
00:03:24,704 --> 00:03:25,204
Ah...

70
00:03:27,832 --> 00:03:29,792
Yeah?

71
00:03:32,337 --> 00:03:33,046
Sorry

72
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:35,506
I'm really sorry

73
00:03:35,506 --> 00:03:36,341
No, it's just...

74
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:38,009
No, I was really wrong

75
00:03:38,009 --> 00:03:38,968
Hey, Yoo Si-hwan...

76
00:03:41,118 --> 00:03:43,836
[Fifth Time Loop]

77
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:47,268
Yeah

78
00:03:47,268 --> 00:03:49,812
I messed it all up

79
00:03:49,812 --> 00:03:51,564
Why did it have to be you?

80
00:03:53,691 --> 00:03:54,984
Why?

81
00:03:55,193 --> 00:03:56,611
No, why did it have to be you?

82
00:03:59,405 --> 00:04:00,490
Why?

83
00:04:00,490 --> 00:04:01,658
Why are you, you?

84
00:04:01,658 --> 00:04:03,368
Ah, why did it have to be you?

85
00:04:03,785 --> 00:04:05,453
Ah, don't say it like that

86
00:04:05,453 --> 00:04:07,747
Why is it you?

87
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,728
[Sixth Time Loop]

88
00:04:12,728 --> 00:04:14,529
[Sixth Time Loop]
Oh, Shit!

89
00:04:19,467 --> 00:04:21,261
I'm going out for a smoke

90
00:04:24,347 --> 00:04:27,183
Since when do you smoke? I've never seen you do it

91
00:04:27,809 --> 00:04:29,727
I just need some fresh air

92
00:04:33,815 --> 00:04:35,608
Hey, Yoo Si-hwan

93
00:05:08,558 --> 00:05:09,183
I'm sorry

94
00:05:11,728 --> 00:05:13,438
I would have been confused too

95
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:15,857
You know I'm prone to loneliness

96
00:05:17,942 --> 00:05:20,194
So, I dared to...

97
00:05:20,194 --> 00:05:22,155
...covet a friend

98
00:05:31,831 --> 00:05:35,418
If you want to stop being friends, that's okay

99
00:05:36,502 --> 00:05:38,463
Hey, that...

100
00:05:40,381 --> 00:05:42,008
Oh, this?

101
00:05:42,342 --> 00:05:44,177
Yeah, it's the bracelet you gave me

102
00:05:47,221 --> 00:05:50,641
But now, only one humble strand remains

103
00:05:50,808 --> 00:05:52,101
I should have cherished it more

104
00:05:58,024 --> 00:06:00,943
Honestly, I'm not confident about not seeing you

105
00:06:01,944 --> 00:06:02,945
So...

106
00:06:03,696 --> 00:06:06,407
I'm thinking of it as my last hope

107
00:06:07,158 --> 00:06:09,535
Contact me when you've cooled down

108
00:06:18,086 --> 00:06:18,586
Hey, Yoo Si-hwan

109
00:06:25,051 --> 00:06:25,968
'Ah...'

110
00:06:25,968 --> 00:06:28,054
'This is the last time...'

111
00:06:29,127 --> 00:06:33,554
[Final Time Loop]

112
00:06:54,163 --> 00:06:56,249
Are you going to keep silent?

113
00:07:03,965 --> 00:07:05,883
Yeah

114
00:07:05,883 --> 00:07:08,428
I like you, Joochan

115
00:07:10,721 --> 00:07:13,266
I don't know since when

116
00:07:13,266 --> 00:07:14,016
but...

117
00:07:16,686 --> 00:07:17,603
I just really like you

118
00:07:26,904 --> 00:07:29,699
When a guy who's been your friend for 7 years says this,

119
00:07:30,241 --> 00:07:32,827
it's natural to react that way

120
00:07:34,078 --> 00:07:35,913
I understand

121
00:07:40,001 --> 00:07:44,213
But these are just my one-sided feelings

122
00:07:44,213 --> 00:07:48,676
so you decide whether we continue seeing each other

123
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:52,388
The one who likes first always loses, right?

124
00:07:55,892 --> 00:07:56,726
Ha

125
00:07:58,436 --> 00:07:59,479
Yoo Si-hwan

126
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:02,315
You bastard

127
00:08:18,456 --> 00:08:21,292
Why did this come back to me?

128
00:08:22,877 --> 00:08:24,670
Why is that there?

129
00:08:28,174 --> 00:08:29,634
Is this the seventh time now?

130
00:08:29,634 --> 00:08:32,720
So, it works like this?

131
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,971
I'll give it a try

132
00:08:34,472 --> 00:08:37,141
You don't remember, do you?

133
00:08:37,141 --> 00:08:39,769
What I said to you at the lake park

134
00:08:41,854 --> 00:08:43,147
What are you talking about?

135
00:08:50,696 --> 00:08:53,115
Why?

136
00:08:53,115 --> 00:08:55,618
Si-hwan.

137
00:08:55,618 --> 00:08:57,954
I like you.

138
00:09:06,462 --> 00:09:09,173
(Si-hwan, I like you.)

139
00:09:09,173 --> 00:09:11,467
(Yu Si-hwan, will you go out with me?)

140
00:09:11,467 --> 00:09:14,011
(Si-hwan, I like you.)

141
00:09:14,011 --> 00:09:17,765
(Yu Si-hwan, I'll take care of you.)

142
00:09:20,059 --> 00:09:24,480
Back then, I confessed to you six times.

143
00:09:28,776 --> 00:09:29,402
And.

144
00:09:30,903 --> 00:09:33,447
In the end, I chose not to confess.

145
00:09:36,367 --> 00:09:41,038
I kept returning to the time before my confession.

146
00:09:41,789 --> 00:09:43,583
But.

147
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:47,211
You, in the end, spoke honestly.

148
00:09:48,838 --> 00:09:49,964
You're better than me.

149
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:57,638
That's why I like you.

150
00:09:59,015 --> 00:09:59,765
I like you.

151
00:10:01,017 --> 00:10:01,934
Yoo Si-hwan.

152
00:10:03,311 --> 00:10:05,313
Oh, it's connected!

153
00:10:05,313 --> 00:10:06,814
Thank you.

154
00:10:06,814 --> 00:10:08,441
Thank you, technician. I love you.

155
00:10:10,568 --> 00:10:13,154
Hey, this is real, right?

156
00:10:13,613 --> 00:10:17,158
It's not some virtual reality or something, right?

157
00:10:17,158 --> 00:10:18,200
What are you saying?

158
00:10:21,037 --> 00:10:22,288
Hey.

159
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:24,248
Come closer.

160
00:10:34,008 --> 00:10:36,010
I came back with your permission.

161
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,306
Don't avoid me.
